Many actual people have made appearances on Seinfeld , Often playing themselves.
[ edit ] Actual people played by others
Appeared in minor speaking roles in more than 20 episodes, including "Ian" in " The Wig Master " and "Man at Airport" in " The Limo ". He appears in the background in many other episodes.
